comment: /**  * Assert the result of an executed request.  * @param result the result of the executed request  * @throws Exception if a failure occurs  */
code: /**  * Assert the result of an executed request.  * @param result the result of the executed request  * @throws Exception if a failure occurs  */ void match(MvcResult result) throws Exception.

comment: /**  * Static method for matching with an array of result matchers.  * @param matchers the matchers  * @since 5.1  */
code: /**  * Static method for matching with an array of result matchers.  * @param matchers the matchers  * @since 5.1  */ static ResultMatcher matchAll(ResultMatcher... matchers) {     return result -> {         for (ResultMatcher matcher : matchers) {             matcher.match(result).         }     }. }
